   <talk_paragraph index="n2578_nophee-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2578_nophee-2-a" mid="16" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe${sound:npc_Nophee_9825_qu_01.ogg}<BR>I was worried that we might not have collected enough mana because of the rushed schedule but I was worried for nothing. The <FONT color=#086171>size of the barrier</FONT> is big enough to cover the entire Merca and as long as <FONT color=#086171>there is a stable supply of mana</FONT>, there wouldn’t be any problem.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2578_nophee-2-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_Salica.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2578_nophee-2-b" mid="18" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>$Shalica$<BR>Thanks, Norfe. Now Merca will be the only state in Mistland that is not threatened by the <FONT color=#a82424>Childs</FONT>. <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>, let’s go to <FONT color=#086171>Vernicka</FONT> now and let him know that the relic is working well.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2578_nophee-2-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2578_nophee-2-c" mid="20" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>What...? I’m coming with you?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2578_nophee-2-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_Salica.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2578_nophee-2-" mid="22" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>$Shalica${sound:npc_Salica_9825_qu_04.ogg}<BR>I’m not the only one who made this happen. I know <FONT color=#086171>Vernicka</FONT> must have been harsh with words and gave you a hard time. Don’t you think this is an opportunity to get his acknowledgements for your achievements?<BR><BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>* Go to </FONT><FONT color=#086171>President Vernicka</FONT><FONT color=#7e12d2> with Shalica.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2585_vernicka-3" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2585_vernicka-3-a" mid="24" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="23"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>……. <FONT color=#7e12d2>(He is looking up at the sky.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2585_vernicka-3-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2585_vernicka-3-b" mid="26" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="25"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Vernicka, did you see that? Relic restoration was a success. Now as long as the force field surrounds Merca, this city will be safe from any harm.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2585_vernicka-3-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_Salica.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2585_vernicka-3-c" mid="28" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="27"><![CDATA[<html>$Shalica${sound:npc_Salica_9825_qu_05.ogg}<BR>We did it. Merca is now going to be free from <FONT color=#a82424>Childs’</FONT> control and write its <FONT color=#086171>new history</FONT>. We have taken our first step in being a completely <FONT color=#086171>independent state</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2585_vernicka-3-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2585_vernicka-3-d" mid="30" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="29"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka${sound:npc_Vernicka_9825_qu_01.ogg}<BR>Oh my goodness... I never knew such a day would come. Never…….</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2585_vernicka-3-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_Salica.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2585_vernicka-3-e" mid="32" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="31"><![CDATA[<html>$Shalica${sound:npc_Salica_9825_qu_06.ogg}<BR>I would have thought so too if I was in this alone. The help I got from <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>, the Anti-Goddess Faction and Norfe, Grele and Geraint, and the wise Red Dragon Rubinart made it possible for us to achieve this. Oh, let’s not forget about Gregory too.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2585_vernicka-3-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_Salica.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2585_vernicka-3-f" mid="34" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="33"><![CDATA[<html>$Shalica${sound:npc_Salica_9825_qu_07.ogg}<BR>And… I also want to thank you, Vernicka, for giving me your trust and waiting patiently all these years.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2585_vernicka-3-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2585_vernicka-3-g" mid="36" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="35"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka${sound:npc_Vernicka_9825_qu_02.ogg}<BR>You’ve shown me much bigger kindness in the past so of course I would do that for you. But what happened in the past worries me. There was a time when Chiron Island’s <FONT color=#a82424>barrier disappeared</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2585_vernicka-3-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2585_vernicka-3-h" mid="38" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="37"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Norfe said that the barrier will work as long as it is supplied with enough magic power.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2585_vernicka-3-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2585_vernicka-3-i" mid="40" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="39"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>Do you think the people of ancient Chiron Island let the barrier disappear because they didn’t know that? There are no <FONT color=#086171>sorcerers</FONT> or <FONT color=#086171>sorceresses</FONT> here in Merca. We don’t have someone who is an expert on magic. Then how would we know if we have a stable supply of mana?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2585_vernicka-3-i" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2585_vernicka-4" mid="42" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="41"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>I’m sure the wise <FONT color=#086171>Lord Norfe</FONT> has thought through this already. He must have a plan in his mind.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2585_vernicka-4" image="QN_Nophee.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2585_vernicka-4-" mid="44" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="43"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>I’m sure Norfe, I mean Lord Norfe, has planned something! Let me go and ask him.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-4" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-4-a" mid="46" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="45"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe${sound:npc_Nophee_9825_qu_02.ogg}<BR>I was about to tell you about that anyway. It is not an easy task for ordinary people to manage <FONT color=#086171>magical devices</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-4-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-4-b" mid="48" select_type="4" />
      <talk_question mid="47"><![CDATA[<html>$Quest Completed$</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-4-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-4-!next" mid="50" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="49"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe$<BR>Mana is an energy that occurs naturally so it tends to change a lot like the weather. Mana can flow freely on some days and dry up on others.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
